eserve list four weeks in advance of the first class meeting will insure the material will be ready for your students please see our faculty course reserves page for the information we need for reserve items the default loan period for reserve items is 2 hours but other loan periods can be arranged on request for more complete information about how to place items on reserve see the faculty course reserves page engineering engineering library group menu back stanford university stanford california 94305 650 725 1064 terms of use copyright complaints
